Posts.Content: I am not a doctor. I am somewhat of an analytical observer. If your father and / or Brothers had prostate cancer you have a much higher probability of getting the disease as well, by my observation. However my mother had breast cancer at a late age of about seventy, my two sisters did not have breast cancer, (but might if they reach seventy) but their daughters did, and at a much younger age. Someone Please write in and summarize the Cancer Genetics web/nar Please.
